table.name: ds4m1_contentitem_tag_map
table.comment: Maps items from content tables to tags

table.name: ds4m1_ucm_content
table.comment: Contains core content data in name spaced fields

column.name: level
column.comment: The cached level in the nested tree.

column.name: name
column.comment: The unique name for the asset.

column.name: title
column.comment: The descriptive title for the asset.

column.name: id
column.comment: A reference to the associated item.

column.name: context
column.comment: The context of the associated item.

column.name: key
column.comment: The key for the association computed from an md5 on associated ids.

column.name: metadesc
column.comment: The meta description for the page.

column.name: metakey
column.comment: The meta keywords for the page.

column.name: xreference
column.comment: A reference to enable linkages to external data sets.

column.name: language
column.comment: The language code for the article.

column.name: xreference
column.comment: A reference to enable linkages to external data sets.

column.name: core_content_id
column.comment: PK from the core content table

column.name: content_item_id
column.comment: PK from the content type table

column.name: tag_date
column.comment: Date of most recent save for this tag-item

index.name: idx_published_list
index.columns: published state access publish_start_date publish_end_date list_price

index.name: idx_published_sale
index.columns: published state access publish_start_date publish_end_date sale_price

column.name: menutype
column.comment: The type of menu this item belongs to. FK to #__menu_types.menutype

column.name: title
column.comment: The display title of the menu item.

column.name: alias
column.comment: The SEF alias of the menu item.

column.name: path
column.comment: The computed path of the menu item based on the alias field.

column.name: link
column.comment: The actually link the menu item refers to.

column.name: type
column.comment: The type of link: Component, URL, Alias, Separator

column.name: published
column.comment: The published state of the menu link.

column.name: parent_id
column.comment: The parent menu item in the menu tree.

column.name: level
column.comment: The relative level in the tree.

column.name: checked_out_time
column.comment: The time the menu item was checked out.

column.name: browserNav
column.comment: The click behaviour of the link.

column.name: access
column.comment: The access level required to view the menu item.

column.name: img
column.comment: The image of the menu item.

column.name: params
column.comment: JSON encoded data for the menu item.

column.name: home
column.comment: Indicates if this menu item is the home or default page.

column.name: xreference
column.comment: A reference to enable linkages to external data sets.

column.name: action_file
column.comment: RAD URI to the PHP file containing action method

column.name: condition_file
column.comment: RAD URI to file holding display condition method

column.name: condition_method
column.comment: Display condition method, must return boolean

column.name: version_introduced
column.comment: Version when this message was introduced

column.name: metadesc
column.comment: The meta description for the page.

column.name: metakey
column.comment: The meta keywords for the page.

column.name: core_type_alias
column.comment: FK to the content types table

column.name: core_content_item_id
column.comment: ID from the individual type table

column.name: core_xreference
column.comment: A reference to enable linkages to external data sets.

column.name: character_count
column.comment: Number of characters in this version.

column.name: sha1_hash
column.comment: SHA1 hash of the version_data column.

column.name: resetCount
column.comment: Count of password resets since lastResetTime

column.name: requireReset
column.comment: Require user to reset password on next login
